trans-unit.source: Represents a cell in the rendered table of a tabular ASP.NET data-bound control, such as <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView"></xref> or <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en cell i tabellen renderade i en tabellvy ASP.NET databunden kontroll som <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The DataControlFieldCell class is a strongly typed <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell> class that represents a cell in ASP.NET data-bound controls that render their contents in a tabular layout, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>.
trans-unit.target: DataControlFieldCell-klassen är en starkt typifierad <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell>klass som representerar en cell i ASP.NET databundna kontroller som återge innehållet i en tabellvy layout, till exempel <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>och <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> object that contains the DataControlFieldCell object controls how the cell is rendered by applying styles to the cell.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>objekt som innehåller objektet DataControlFieldCell styr hur cellen återges genom att använda formatmallar i cellen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>

trans-unit.source: You can access the containing <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> object using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell.ContainingField%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Du kan komma åt den innehållande <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>objekt med den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell.ContainingField%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell.ContainingField%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell"></xref> class, setting the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"></xref> object as the cell's container.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell"> </xref> klass, ställa in den angivna <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"> </xref> objekt som den cellen behållare.

trans-unit.source: This constructor uses the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag?displayProperty=fullName> element defined by its base class to render the cell.
trans-unit.target: Den här konstruktorn använder den <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag?displayProperty=fullName>element som har definierats av dess basklass ska renderas i cellen.</xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> object passed in the `containingField` parameter is used to determine whether to show headers and what styles to apply to the cell when it is rendered.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>objekt skickades den `containingField` används för att avgöra om du vill visa rubriker och vad formatmallar ska gälla för cellen när den återges.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"></xref> that contains the current cell.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"> </xref> som innehåller den aktiva cellen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell"></xref> class, setting the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"></xref> object as the cell's container.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell"> </xref> klass, ställa in den angivna <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"> </xref> objekt som den cellen behållare.

trans-unit.source: The `tagKey` parameter is passed to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl> base class constructor, and controls the HTML tag that is emitted by the control.
trans-unit.target: Den `tagKey` parameter har skickats till den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl>base klasskonstruktor och kontroller HTML-tagg som genereras av kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> passed in the `containingField` parameter is used to determine whether to show headers and what styles to apply to the cell when it is rendered.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>skickades den `containingField` används för att avgöra om du vill visa rubriker och vad formatmallar ska gälla för cellen när den återges.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag"></xref> that specifies the HTML tag to render for the cell.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag"> </xref> som anger HTML-taggen ska renderas i cellen.

trans-unit.source: The default tag used by the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell"></xref> class is <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standardetiketten som används av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell"> </xref> klass är <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"></xref> that contains the current cell.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"> </xref> som innehåller den aktiva cellen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"></xref> object that contains the current cell.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"> </xref> objekt som innehåller den aktiva cellen.

trans-unit.source: The content rendering for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell> object might be affected by the various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> properties of the containing field, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ItemStyle%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ControlStyle%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ShowHeader%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Innehåll rendering för den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell>objekt kan påverkas av de olika <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>Egenskaper för den som innehåller fält som <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ItemStyle%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ControlStyle%2A>, och <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ShowHeader%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ShowHeader%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ControlStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ItemStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"></xref> that contains the current cell, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>, if no <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"></xref> is passed to the class constructor.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"> </xref> som innehåller den aktuella cellen eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>, om ingen <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"> </xref> har överförts till klasskonstruktorn.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies whether the control validates client input.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger ett värde som anger om kontrollen verifierar klienten indata.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the control validates client input; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om kontrollen verifierar klienten indata; Annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
